SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Address], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[DeletedAt], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[FirstName], [t].[HireDate], [t].[LastName], [t].[Phone], [t].[UpdatedAt], [d].[Id], [d].[CreatedAt], [d].[DeletedAt], [d].[Name], [d].[UpdatedAt]
FROM (
    SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[Address], [e].[CreatedAt], [e].[DeletedAt], [e].[DepartmentId], [e].[FirstName], [e].[HireDate], [e].[LastName], [e].[Phone], [e].[UpdatedAt]
    FROM [Employees] AS [e]

          FROM [Employees] AS [e]
          WHERE [e].[DeletedAt] IS NULL
          ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
          OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
      ) AS [t]
      INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d] ON [t].[DepartmentId] = [d].[Id]
